                            <comment id="23950" author="balex" created="Wed, 23 May 2007 11:16:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Similar issue exists in AbstractProcessingFilter.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="23951" author="balex" created="Wed, 23 May 2007 11:18:22 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I am hesitant to change to equals() because we ended up with endsWith() because of various servlet container implementation inconsistencies. So, I&apos;ve modified both LogoutFilter and AbstractProcessingFilter to use the following fragment of code:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;        if (&quot;&quot;.equals(request.getContextPath())) &lt;/p&gt;
{
        	return uri.endsWith(filterProcessesUrl);
        }

&lt;p&gt;        return uri.endsWith(request.getContextPath() + filterProcessesUrl);&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Checked into SVN revision 1855.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="23963" author="jbq" created="Wed, 23 May 2007 19:51:42 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I don&apos;t know of any inconsistency WRT request.getContextPath(), and correct me if I&apos;m wrong but:&lt;/p&gt;

